            <title>[MSHADE-98] minimizeJar option excludes package-info classes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/MSHADE-98</link>
                <project id="12317921" key="MSHADE">Maven Shade Plugin (Moved to GitHub Issues)</project>
